Title: Last Rites By Accident
Description: <You can hear the faint sound of screaming coming from the other side of the portal.>
ObjectivesText: Go through the Demonic Gateway and help the Initiates.
RewardText:
The others... their soulstones...

I saw a green flicker in their eyes as they fell, one by one. Like the very essence of their souls were being drawn forth.

They deserved better.
